SELECT u.user_id, ua.address, ua.city, ua.state, ua.country FROM user_addresses ua JOIN user_locations ul ON ua.user_id = ul.user_id JOIN map_markers mm ON ul.user_id = mm.user_id WHERE mm.marker_name = 'Home' ORDER BY ua.city DESC, mm.marker_name ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT uu.user_id, ua.address, ua.city, gd.latitude, gd.longitude FROM user_addresses ua JOIN user_locations ul ON ua.user_id = ul.user_id JOIN geocoding_data gd ON ul.geocoding_id = gd.geocoding_id JOIN (SELECT user_id FROM user_locations GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 2) AS uu ON ua.user_id = uu.user_id ORDER BY gd.accuracy DESC, ua.state ASC;

SELECT ua.user_id, ua.address, ua.city, ua.state, ua.country, gd.latitude, gd.longitude FROM user_addresses ua LEFT JOIN geocoding_data gd ON ua.user_id = gd.user_id WHERE gd.latitude IS NOT NULL AND gd.longitude IS NOT NULL ORDER BY ua.user_id ASC;

SELECT ua.user_id, ua.address, ua.city, gd.latitude, gd.longitude FROM user_addresses ua JOIN geocoding_data gd ON ua.user_id = gd.user_id WHERE gd.accuracy > 80 AND ua.state = 'California' ORDER BY ua.user_id ASC, gd.accuracy DESC;

SELECT mm.marker_id, mm.user_id, ul.location_id, ua.address, ua.city, gd.latitude, gd.longitude, mm.marker_name FROM map_markers mm JOIN user_locations ul ON mm.location_id = ul.location_id JOIN user_addresses ua ON ul.address_id = ua.address_id JOIN geocoding_data gd ON ul.geocoding_id = gd.geocoding_id WHERE gd.accuracy > 70 AND ua.country = 'USA' ORDER BY gd.accuracy DESC, mm.marker_name ASC;
